quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  32,23,“Ndipo ndithu Mûsa tidampatsa buku. Choncho usakhale ndi chikaiko pa zakukumana Naye (Allah). Ndipo tidalichita (bukulo) kukhala chiongoko cha ana a Israyeli
  32,24,"“Ndipo ena mwa iwo tidawachita kukhala atsogoleri oongola (anthu) mwa lamulo lathu, pamene adapirira; ndipo adali kuvomereza motsimikiza Ayah Zathu"
  32,25,“Ndithudi Mbuye wako ndi Yemwe adzaweruze pakati pawo tsiku la Qiyâma pazimene amatsutsana
  32,26,"“Kodi sizidadziwike kwa iwo kuti ndimibadwo ingati imene tidaiononga patsogolo pawo; (chikhalirecho iwo) akudutsa mokhala mwawo? Ndithu m’zimenezo, muli zizindikiro, kodi sakumva"
  32,27,“Kodi sakuona kuti timapereka madzi ku nthaka youma; ndipo ndi madziwo tikumeretsa mrnera umene ziweto zawo zimadya ndi iwo omwe; kodi sakupenya
  32,28,"“Ndipo akunena: “Kulamulidwa kumeneku (kwa tsiku la chimaliziro) kudzachitika liti, ngati mukunenadi zoona?”"
  32,29,"“Nena: “Tsiku la chiweruzirolo, amene sadakhulupirire, chikhulupiriro chawo sichidzawathandiza. Ndipo sadzapatsidwa nthawi yoyembekezera (kuti mizimu yawo isachoke ayambe akhulupirira kaye, mngero wa imfa akadzawadzera).”"
  32,30,“Choncho apatuke; ndipo yembekezera (zimene Allah wakulonjeza). Ndithu nawonso akuyembekezera (zimene Allah wawalonjeza)